{"tid":340931,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知點樣可以練到擒拿手？","createTime":"2017-07-30T11:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T01:17:14.000Z","uid":342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce447fb399e54ac4c825dae460a12318c21ad8b2","tid":340931,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:03:24.000Z","msg":"呢排間唔中就有顛佬出現<br />\n又打人 有時又有架生<br />\n啲蝻又無法無天咁<br />\n但有單新聞就話有男途人出黎幫拖比人拉鳩左<br />\n<br />\n咁我就諗<br />\n點樣可以幫拖而又唔使令差佬覺得係打緊交呢？<br />\n<br />\n1.柔道<br />\n<br />\n柔道用黎制服人 <br />\n實用程度就眾所鳩知<br />\n泡菜啲差佬都用<br />\n不過技巧高 要練一排先可以係實戰中用到<br />\n而且柔道要貼實晒 胸貼胸咁都幾恐佈<br />\n而且係硬地達鳩人 一陣達撚到重傷就仆街 又係要比差佬拉（利申試過）<br />\n不過大家可以練住先<br />\n<br />\n2.練兵器<br />\n<br />\n比你練成左仲衰<br />\n還拖隨時變左誤殺<br />\n<br />\n3.擒拿手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該一野捉到條友隻手就gg<br />\n再發力捉實 條友手都軟埋<br />\n仲簡單過柔道<br />\n捉實再發力就得<br />\n想問下香港有冇地方教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923f99dcfcf57727b8e2da43d524d5ed21158d50","tid":340931,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:10:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ede5bafec5473e00b99482074c3a55ecb684e102","tid":340931,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08dd82bdf05fc618bd6dae18b7b6774686646b36","tid":340931,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T13:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ff9d6a553794fd51ca5ed0ea09db7b176a6653","tid":340931,"uid":64798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T13:57:28.000Z","msg":"搏擊lo"},{"pid":"0889ab57468a3a37ebd9a43a576e32c43d3f4918","tid":340931,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搏擊lo</blockquote><br />\n搏擊唔係拳拳到肉架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好大分別bo"},{"pid":"063bf42342347b6e43b339b8081ac06c9f6c4d4d","tid":340931,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T15:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/234414_3b7c2f439bc13b2ffaf13e1bb42ed40e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F234414_3b7c2f439bc13b2ffaf13e1bb42ed40e.jpg&h=7f36e066&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f89ae06b88f033938d7f56931d3681e45440fdf2","tid":340931,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T16:28:36.000Z","msg":"詠春有招從後鎖人<br />\n面向對方背部<br />\n雙手穿過對方胳肋底<br />\n雙手喺對方頸後扣緊<br />\n基本上鎖到嘅話，對方好難解鎖<br />\n<br />\n不過唔知道就咁鎖住佢，冇打佢，會唔會比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43b4b99353c8dc0cedf449cdcf916c6164ae790","tid":340931,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T17:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>詠春有招從後鎖人<br />\n面向對方背部<br />\n雙手穿過對方胳肋底<br />\n雙手喺對方頸後扣緊<br />\n基本上鎖到嘅話，對方好難解鎖<br />\n<br />\n不過唔知道就咁鎖住佢，冇打佢，會唔會比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你講個個鎖如果成功使出<br />\n應該冇殺傷力之餘鎖得好實架<br />\n咁都比人拉真係以後有咩事報警等警犬慢慢搞了"},{"pid":"c6c11e2857ca83166b562c56448ff31613e4898c","tid":340931,"uid":18105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"基本上你有動作掂到對方既身體都可以告你普通襲擊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：毒law"},{"pid":"35b8993743a5ed60b8878def375f1af5dc9eccd2","tid":340931,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基本上你有動作掂到對方既身體都可以告你普通襲擊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：毒law</blockquote><br />\n吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}